            "row_content": "<p>Follow these steps to initiate a return:</p><p><strong>1. Contact Us:</strong></p><ul><li>Email our customer support team at <strong>[EMAIL]</strong> with your order number and reason for the return.</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>2. Approval:<br/><br/></strong>Once your request is reviewed, we will approve or decline the return request within <strong>3 business days</strong>.</p><ul><li>If approved, we will provide you with return instructions and the return shipping address.</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>3. Shipping the Item:<br/></strong></p><ul><li>Package the product securely to prevent damage during transit.</li><li>You are responsible for the cost of return shipping unless the return is due to a defective or incorrect product.</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>4. Confirmation:<br/><br/></strong>Once we receive and inspect the returned item, we will notify you of the approval or rejection of your refund.</p>",
